This is a map i made a while ago for a mod called ISS itchy and scratchy source. the mod failed and I'm releasing the map so here it is. The map originally had mines that if you walk over them u would blow up but i removed them although may add them in as a new type of gamestyle if people wish.
i recommend about 12 - 24 players 
there is no nav file although chiz may nav it soon im sure the default nav will work fine  
I know it looks weird with a mixture of cartoonish textures and real textures i tried to model some cars for this but i could not get them to work in game or texture properly sorry.
